review 1:
I have stayed in this place for a few days this week.

Such a quiet very nice place surrounded by natural forrest and rice field. I would highly recommend this place if you are looking for a highclass peacefull vacation.

Will certainly come back. See you soon thank you soo very much Bernardette and Paul.
